## Angular 21 Modern Patterns

### Signals (Preferred)
```typescript
// State
count = signal(0);
doubled = computed(() => this.count() * 2);

// Updates
this.count.set(5);
this.count.update(c => c + 1);
```

### Zoneless Change Detection
- Use `provideZonelessChangeDetection()` in app config
- All state changes via signals trigger UI updates automatically
- No need for `zone.js` or `ChangeDetectorRef`

### Control Flow
```html
@if (isLoading()) {
  <app-skeleton />
} @else {
  <app-content [data]="data()" />
}

@for (item of items(); track item.id) {
  <app-card [item]="item" />
} @empty {
  <app-empty-state />
}
```
